PrecisCANADIAN FORCES 1992 INCOME TAX REMISSION ORDER - which effectively allows members of the Canadian Armed Forces who are part of or serve in immediate support of a number of United Nations military operations to make late contributions to registered retirement savings plans (RRSP) for 1992 on or before October 31, 1993, without penalties.
